Fees.Borrow Interest: All interest paid by borrowers from all markets (excluding USDXL).
Fees.Borrow Interest USDXL: All interest paid by borrowers from USDXL only.
Fees.Flashloan Fees: Flashloan fees paid by flashloan borrowers and executors.
Fees.Liquidation Fees: Fees from liquidation penalty and bonuses.

ProtocolRevenue.Borrow Interest: Amount of interest distributed to lenders from all markets (excluding USDXL) are collected by HypurrFi treasury.
ProtocolRevenue.Borrow Interest USDXL: All interest paid on USDXL market are collected by HypurrFi treasury.
ProtocolRevenue.Flashloan Fees: A portion of fees paid by flashloan borrowers and executors are collected by HypurrFi treasury.
ProtocolRevenue.Liquidation Fees: A portion of fees from liquidation penalty and bonuses are colected by HypurrFi treasury.

Revenue.Borrow Interest: A portion of interest paid by borrowers from all markets (excluding USDXL).
Revenue.Borrow Interest USDXL: All 100% interest paid by USDXL borrowers.
Revenue.Flashloan Fees: A portion of fees paid by flashloan borrowers and executors.
Revenue.Liquidation Fees: A portion of fees from liquidation penalty and bonuses.

SupplySideRevenue.Borrow Interest: Amount of interest distributed to lenders from all markets (excluding USDXL).
SupplySideRevenue.Borrow Interest USDXL: No supply side revenue for lenders on USDXL market.
SupplySideRevenue.Flashloan Fees: Flashloan fees paid by flashloan borrowers and executors are distributed to lenders.
SupplySideRevenue.Liquidation Fees: Fees from liquidation penalty and bonuses are distributed to lenders.
